            mda-type me12-100gb-qsfp28
            sync-e

                        bandwidth 40
                    exit
                exit
            exit
            no shutdown
        exit

            ingress
                dist-cpu-protection
                    dynamic-enforcement-policer-pool 32000
                exit
            exit
        exit
        no shutdown
    exit

            description "VPOP Security Policy"

echo "Bfd Configuration"

        bfd
            begin

                transmit-interval 1000
                receive-interval 1000
            exit

        exit
        policy-options
            begin
            prefix-list "OSS"
            exit
            prefix-list "ECMP"
                prefix 10.20.1.1/32 exact
            exit
            prefix-list "IANA"
                prefix 0.0.0.0/0 through 6
                prefix 0.0.0.0/8 through 32
                prefix 100.64.0.0/10 through 32
                prefix 127.0.0.0/8 through 32
                prefix 169.254.0.0/16 through 32

                prefix 224.0.0.0/3 through 32
            exit
            prefix-list "DIRECT"
                prefix 10.193.59.4/31 exact
                prefix 10.193.59.6/31 exact
                prefix 10.193.59.16/31 exact
                prefix 154.11.131.30/31 exact
                prefix 172.25.99.178/31 exact
                prefix 172.25.99.178/31 longer
                prefix 209.89.78.128/29 longer
            exit
            prefix-list "LI-DF3"
                prefix 172.21.65.160/28 exact
            exit
            prefix-list "SYS_IP"
                prefix 172.25.141.27/32 exact
            exit
            prefix-list "DEFAULT"
                prefix 0.0.0.0/0 exact
            exit
            prefix-list "IANA-BI"
                prefix 0.0.0.0/0 through 6
                prefix 0.0.0.0/8 longer
                prefix 0.0.0.0/8 through 32
                prefix 127.0.0.0/8 longer
                prefix 127.0.0.0/8 through 32
                prefix 169.254.0.0/16 longer
                prefix 169.254.0.0/16 through 32
                prefix 192.0.0.0/24 longer
                prefix 192.0.0.0/24 through 32
                prefix 192.0.2.0/24 longer
                prefix 192.0.2.0/24 through 32
                prefix 198.18.0.0/15 longer
                prefix 198.18.0.0/15 through 32
                prefix 198.51.100.0/24 longer
                prefix 198.51.100.0/24 through 32
                prefix 203.0.113.0/24 longer
                prefix 203.0.113.0/24 through 32
                prefix 224.0.0.0/3 longer
                prefix 224.0.0.0/3 through 32
            exit
            prefix-list "RFC1918"
                prefix 10.0.0.0/8 longer
